"title": "8257: fruitfulness, natural",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8257",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>In the OT fruitfulness is often used as a way of referring to God's material and physical blessings.</p>\n<h2>God's blessing on creation generally</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:11-Gen1:12\">GEN 1:11–1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:22\">GEN 1:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:17\">GEN 8:17</a></p>\n<h2>Fruitfulness in the promised land</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:18-Lev25:19\">LEV 25:18–25:19</a></strong> <em>God's blessing was seen in terms of material prosperity.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:3-Lev26:4\">LEV 26:3–26:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:13\">DEU 32:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:13-Deut33:16\">DEU 33:13–33:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:27\">EZK 34:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:14\">AMO 9:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:12\">ZEC 8:12</a></p>\n<h2>Fruitfulness in family relationships</h2>\n<h3>Such fruitfulness promised</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:16\">GEN 13:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:5\">GEN 15:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:6\">GEN 17:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:20\">GEN 17:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:17\">GEN 22:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:9\">LEV 26:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:13\">DEU 7:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:4\">DEU 28:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:11\">DEU 28:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:9\">DEU 30:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps128:3\">PSA 128:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:3\">JER 23:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:11\">EZK 36:11</a></p>\n<h3>Such fruitfulness commanded</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:28\">GEN 1:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:1\">GEN 9:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:7\">GEN 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:11\">GEN 35:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:3-Gen48:4\">GEN 48:3–48:4</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of such fruitfulness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:24\">PSA 105:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:52\">GEN 41:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:27\">GEN 47:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:22\">GEN 49:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:7\">EXO 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:37-Ps107:38\">PSA 107:37–107:38</a></p>",
